Invicta Reserve 52mm Bolt Zeus "Twisted Metal" Swiss Made Quartz Chronograph Polyurethane Strap WatchBlack accents Invicta's Reserve Bolt Zeus doesn't take any punches. Especially not the Swiss made "Twisted Metal" edition.It lands on your wrist with a round stainless steel case and a unidirectional rotating bezel. It's strength and style all rolled into one with the signature Bolt cable wire twisted on top, the Reserve "R" on the crown and Invicta's winged logo etched on the left. More cable wires accent the black strap as it keeps you comfortable and doesn't weigh you down. A round dial powers a 1/10th-seconds subdial near 2:00, a date window near 4:00, a seconds subdial above 6:00 and a 30-minute subdial near 10:00. Luminous Tritnite on the index markers lets you glance and go in any light as the chronograph hand flaunts one more "R" on its end.
